          <text id="/referral_follow_up/referral_follow_up/did_not_go/complete_referral:label">
            <value>ASK: Do you think you need to complete this referral?</value>
          </text>
          <text id="/referral_follow_up/referral_follow_up/did_not_go/discuss_reasons:label">
            <value>Discuss the reasons, and try to solve the problems through advice, and plan how the client may get services.</value>
          </text>
